                                I was born in Zaria, where every challenge carried a hidden lesson. My father’s passing during my early years taught me responsibility early in life. Though resources were limited, imagination and determination became my true wealth. Even as a child, I found ways to turn simplicity into purpose — a spark that shaped the dreamer I’ve become.                            </p>
                            
                            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-900/20 to-amber-800/20 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-amber-500">
                                <p class="italic text-amber-200">
