                                </p>
                            </div>
                            
                            <p class="text-lg">
                                My mother remarried a man who would redefine my understanding of fatherhood. A father who saw potential where others saw limitation. When we were searching for schools, he took us to El-Amin International School. I saw television and the surroundings, and I knew - this is the future of education.
                            </p>
                        </div>
